# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [Unreleased]

### Added
- New feature or enhancement
- New components or modules

### Changed
- Updates or improvements to existing features
- Changes to API or behavior

### Fixed
- Bug fixes and issue resolutions

### Deprecated
- Features or APIs that are deprecated and will be removed in future releases

### Removed
- Features or components that have been removed

## [1.0.0] - 2024-07-20

### Added
- Initial release of the project
- Core components including Button, Icon Button, Card, and more

### Changed
- Improved component styling and layout
- Updated documentation with usage examples

### Fixed
- Resolved minor bugs in Button component
- Fixed issues with CSS conflicts in the Icon Button component

## [0.9.0] - 2024-06-15

### Added
- Added experimental components for feedback
- Included basic theming support

### Changed
- Refactored internal codebase for better maintainability
- Improved performance for data-table component

### Fixed
- Corrected display issues in the data-table header
- Fixed alignment issues in the navigation bar

## [0.8.0] - 2024-05-01

### Added
- New data-grid component with customizable columns
- Integration with external CSS frameworks

### Changed
- Updated design system for consistency
- Improved accessibility features

### Fixed
- Resolved layout issues in the modal component
- Fixed bugs related to dynamic content loading

## [0.7.0] - 2024-03-10

### Added
- Added support for multiple languages
- Introduced user-friendly form components

### Changed
- Refined component API for ease of use
- Enhanced performance for large data sets

### Fixed
- Fixed bugs in the date-picker component
- Corrected minor styling issues

## [0.6.0] - 2024-01-15

### Added
- Added documentation for API usage
- Introduced new icons and visual assets

### Changed
- Improved responsiveness of layout components
- Updated build process for faster development

### Fixed
- Addressed security vulnerabilities
- Fixed issues with form validation

## [0.5.0] - 2023-11-20

### Added
- Added support for custom themes
- Included new utility functions for easier development

### Changed
- Refactored component code for better readability
- Updated dependencies to latest versions

### Fixed
- Resolved minor bugs and issues from previous releases
- Fixed performance issues in the grid component

## [0.4.0] - 2023-09-05

### Added
- Initial alpha release of core components
- Basic setup for project structure and build tools

### Changed
- Improved initial setup instructions
- Enhanced compatibility with popular browsers

### Fixed
- Fixed initial bugs reported during alpha testing
- Addressed setup issues for new contributors

